    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1169294340">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1169294340" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1169294340" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1169294340">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/52075541/">呐</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-03-25</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">与孔广森《补注》并为大戴记最重要的两个清人本子。毕论录文献扫读。粗粗印象是大戴记汇集性质明显，体例上有语录对话也有类《礼记》的解说性质篇目。儒家资料集合一种。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="514058639">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-514058639" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-514058639" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="514058639">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/leoyin1989/">白鹇</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2012-05-04</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">大戴真是不如小戴，散逸大半，剩下的39篇内容平平，完全没小戴那么异彩纷呈。而且后人篡伪甚多，说是戴德选编古礼85篇而成，结果里面居然提到了秦始皇。。。。明显是两汉儒生的手笔。梁任公断言礼记全为两汉之前的，不知他说的是小戴还是大小戴。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="428779352">
