                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">半是精华半是糟，犹可一读，佚失亦憾事。令人惊奇的是，提到了胎教与&#39;君子之于子，爱而勿面也，使而勿貌也，导之以道而勿强也 &#39;，善。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="180780737">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-180780737" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-180780737" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="180780737">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/linzhenyue/">子岳</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2010-09-24</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">這註釋有待加強啊，精華還沒加進來</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
